<dl id="n53034v"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n53" href="#n53034v">N53 (VI.B.46)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n53all.htm#n53034v"> 34(v)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> ~ Haman Aman, </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: The Feast of Purim (from the Assyrian word for &lsquo;lot&rsquo; &mdash; puru) is a Spring celebration. It marks the massacre of the Jews by the Persians in 473 BC as related in the Book of Esther (9.26ff) and of their deliverance from Haman&apos;s seeking to exterminate them (in an early Final Solution). </mm> </dd></dl>
